    {"question": "Does Xero integrate with Stripe?", "answer": "Yes — Xero has a native Stripe integration that automatically imports Stripe payout data, categorizes transactions by type (sales, refunds, fees), and reconciles Stripe payouts to your bank account. For SaaS startups processing subscription revenue through Stripe, this integration eliminates the most time-consuming reconciliation task in monthly bookkeeping."},
